==Afgan s tmezra tussnant==
[[Tmezra n Darwin]]d tmezra udjut tili lɛaks n ajjaden ajennanen,nnun Imallan d Afgan d imeddureb akk-nnsen igun s amelli s lxaleit udjut zgemmi igemgendad n iseggasen,d Afgan af awal-nsen yeqreb s ibiddan imennajen am [[Cambanzi]],[[Bunubu]],[[Ɣurella]],d[[Urang utan]],nnun imessanen dis daddi udjun n Afgan d Cambanzi zgemmi 6 n igendad n iseggasen di [[Ifriqia]].
Ded Afgan d Amelli Abyuluji,ɣres guda n tɣawsiwin am imedduren yiḍen am [[Allel]],d[[Meslan]],d[[Ibebbicen]],d Ifessen d Iḍaren, terni n [[Ḥemḍ nawawi,DNA]]d Mitukundrya d guda n amidyaten yiḍen,dis guda n imessanen tetḥawmen mammu niten daddi n Afgan

==Afgan s tmezra tajeddant==
Ajjed yenna [[Ayrad]] yegu Afgan s tɣuri,imira yegu dis Iman,saha yesar Afgan s tmezri n Ajjeddan Ajennanen,Islam,Tamsiḥit,Tyudayt,
Di Islam yennu Quran Ayrad yegu Adam s tɣuri,imira iguC s tɣezdist n Adam,d sis-en usuned medden,arrawen ajeddanen nnun Adam d Ḥawwa,llan zeddɣen di Tawertit,alemmi tcun s tameddekt,Ayrad yesuffeɣ-ten sis an tamurt.
